<div id="offset-calculator" class="bg-[--color-calc-bg] border-2 border-[--color-calc-border] p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm mb-6 w-full max-w-[620px]">
<h3 class="text-base font-bold bg-[--color-calc-heading] text-[--color-text-dark] px-2 py-1 -mx-4 -mt-4 mb-4 rounded-t-md">Single Wheel Details</h3>
<form onsubmit="calculator.calculateEquivalents(this); return false;" onreset="calculator.clearall();">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-2">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <label for="wheelWidth" class="font-bold whitespace-nowrap">Wheel width</label>
    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">(<abbr title="inches">in.</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="wheelWidth" name="wheelWidth" size="4" class="ml-auto w-16 px-2 py-1 text-right rounded border border-gray-300 shadow-inner text-sm bg-[#FFE4B5] md:py-0.5" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <label for="offset" class="font-bold whitespace-nowrap">Wheel offset</label>
    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="offset" name="offset" size="4" class="ml-auto w-16 px-2 py-1 text-right rounded border border-gray-300 shadow-inner text-sm bg-[#FFE4B5] md:py-0.5" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <label for="diameter" class="font-bold whitespace-nowrap">Wheel diameter</label>
    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">(<abbr title="inches">in.</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="diameter" name="diameter" size="4" class="ml-auto w-16 px-2 py-1 text-right rounded border border-gray-300 shadow-inner text-sm bg-[#F0F0F0] md:py-0.5" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <label for="spacers" class="font-bold whitespace-nowrap">Spacers</label>
    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">(<abbr title="millimetres">mm</abbr>)</span>
    <input type="text" id="spacers" name="spacers" size="4" value="0" class="ml-auto w-16 px-2 py-1 text-right rounded border border-gray-300 shadow-inner text-sm bg-[#F0F0F0] md:py-0.5" />
  </div>
</div>
<div class="text-center py-4">
  <input type="submit" class="button" value="Calculate" />&nbsp;
  <input type="reset" class="button" value="Reset" />
</div>
</form>
<div id="comparison" class="results"></div>
</div>

<div id="description" class="text-[--color-text-dark] text-base leading-relaxed">
<h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">About the Equivalent Arch Clearance Calculator</h2>
<p class="mb-4">The equivalent arch clearance calculator allows you to compare a specified wheel against other wheel sizes with the same arch clearance.</p>
<p class="mb-4">Once you have entered the wheel specification into the form on the left, the calculator will display the equivalent offset of wheels in various widths.</p>
<p class="mb-4">For example, you can calculate that a 9.5J et12 wheel would have the same arch clearance as an 8J et-7 wheel.</p>
<p><a href="javascript:calculator.demo('offset-comparison', 0);" class="text-[--color-link] hover:text-[--color-link-hover] underline">Click for a demo!</a></p>
</div>
